    modified_response: "I will create the `/src/components/LandingPage.tsx` component. It features a modern gaming dashboard design with sharp polygonal shapes, fiery neon orange/crimson gradients, a login form using the unique ID Guild, active stats (e.g. Total Guilds, Active Members, Total Scrim Announcements), and links for registering a new Guild or joining an existing one."
