    modified_response: "I will create the `/src/components/RegisterMember.tsx` component. It provides the form for standard squad members to register into a specific Guild. They can select from a dropdown list of currently active Guilds in our system or input a unique ID Guild manually. It inputs comprehensive gamer profile fields (Full Name, Age, FF Account Level, Home City, and In-game Nickname). On submission, it creates their account with the default role of \"Member\" and offers a celebratory esports welcome card."
