    user_response: "Apply the \"Immersive UI\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Immersive UI\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"flex h-[768px] w-[1024px] flex-col bg-[#020617] text-slate-100 font-sans overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- Top Navigation Bar -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"flex h-16 w-full items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/80 px-8 backdrop-blur-md\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"h-8 w-8 rounded-lg bg-orange-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-black\\\">FF</div>\\n      <span class=\\\"text-xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase italic text-orange-500\\\">Guild Hub FF</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-end\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Logged in as</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-sm font-semibold text-orange-400\\\">KAPTEN_GARUDA <span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-orange-600/20 px-1.5 rounded border border-orange-500/30 ml-1\\\">KETUA</span></span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"h-10 w-10 rounded-full border-2 border-orange-500 p-0.5\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"h-full w-full rounded-full bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center\\\">ID</div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <!-- Main Content Layout -->\\n  <main class=\\\"flex flex-1 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <!-- Sidebar -->\\n    <aside class=\\\"w-64 border-r border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/50 p-6 flex flex-col gap-8\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-1\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2\\\">Menu Utama</p>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg bg-orange-500/10 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-orange-500 border-l-2 border-orange-500\\\">\\n          Dashboard\\n        </button>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-800/50\\\">\\n          Daftar Anggota\\n        </button>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-800/50\\\">\\n          Pengumuman\\n        </button>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-800/50\\\">\\n          Pengaturan Guild\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"mt-auto rounded-xl bg-slate-900/80 p-4 border border-slate-800 shadow-lg\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Guild ID</p>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-lg font-mono font-bold text-white\\\">FF-INDO-99</p>\\n        <button class=\\\"mt-3 w-full rounded bg-slate-800 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors uppercase\\\">Salin Link Invite</button>\\n      </div>\\n    </aside>\\n\\n    <!-- Content Area -->\\n    <section class=\\\"flex-1 p-8 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <!-- Stats Row -->\\n      <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-6\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"rounded-2xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-5 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute -right-2 -top-2 h-16 w-16 bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-2xl\\\"></div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase\\\">Total Member</p>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-3xl font-black mt-1\\\">48<span class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-600 font-medium ml-1\\\">/ 50</span></h3>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"rounded-2xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-5 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute -right-2 -top-2 h-16 w-16 bg-orange-500/5 rounded-full blur-2xl\\\"></div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase\\\">Avg. Level</p>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-3xl font-black mt-1 text-orange-500\\\">LV. 64</h3>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"rounded-2xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-5 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute -right-2 -top-2 h-16 w-16 bg-red-500/5 rounded-full blur-2xl\\\"></div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase\\\">Tournament Win</p>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-3xl font-black mt-1 text-red-500\\\">12</h3>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Split Sections -->\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 grid grid-cols-5 gap-6 min-h-0\\\">\\n        <!-- Mading (Noticeboard) -->\\n        <div class=\\\"col-span-3 flex flex-col rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 px-6 py-4\\\">\\n            <h4 class=\\\"font-black uppercase italic tracking-wider text-orange-500\\\">Mading Guild</h4>\\n            <button class=\\\"rounded bg-orange-600 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-black hover:bg-orange-500\\\">+ Tambah</button>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 p-6 space-y-4 overflow-y-auto\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-4\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2\\\">\\n                <h5 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-white\\\">Scrim Internal @ 20:00 WIB</h5>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">2 Jam Lalu</span>\\n              </div>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed italic\\\">Wajib hadir semua core team untuk persiapan Tourney Season depan. Map: Bermuda & Purgatory.</p>\\n              <div class=\\\"mt-3 flex gap-2\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\\\">#SCRIM</span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-red-500/10 text-red-400 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\\\">#IMPORTANT</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-4 opacity-75\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2\\\">\\n                <h5 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight\\\">Pendaftaran Tourney Regional</h5>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Kemarin</span>\\n              </div>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\\\">Silahkan hubungi Officer untuk pendaftaran slot 1 dan slot 2 paling lambat jam 10 malam ini.</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Member List -->\\n        <div class=\\\"col-span-2 flex flex-col rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 px-6 py-4\\\">\\n            <h4 class=\\\"font-black uppercase italic tracking-wider text-slate-400\\\">Daftar Anggota</h4>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 p-4 overflow-y-auto\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg bg-slate-800/30 p-3 border border-transparent hover:border-slate-700 transition-all\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n                  <div class=\\\"h-8 w-8 rounded bg-orange-500/20 text-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs\\\">G</div>\\n                  <div>\\n                    <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">Garuda_Raja</p>\\n                    <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Jakarta \342\200\242 Lv. 72</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[9px] font-bold text-orange-500 bg-orange-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase\\\">Officer</span>\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg bg-slate-800/30 p-3 border border-transparent hover:border-slate-700 transition-all\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n                  <div class=\\\"h-8 w-8 rounded bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs\\\">M</div>\\n                  <div>\\n                    <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">Mist_Hunter</p>\\n                    <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Bandung \342\200\242 Lv. 65</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[9px] font-bold text-slate-500 bg-slate-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase\\\">Member</span>\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg bg-slate-800/30 p-3 border border-transparent hover:border-slate-700 transition-all\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n                  <div class=\\\"h-8 w-8 rounded bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs\\\">S</div>\\n                  <div>\\n                    <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">Sniper_Elite</p>\\n                    <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Surabaya \342\200\242 Lv. 58</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[9px] font-bold text-slate-500 bg-slate-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase\\\">Member</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- Visual Overlay Background Elements (Simulated) -->\\n  <div class=\\\"fixed -bottom-32 -left-32 h-96 w-96 bg-orange-600/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none\\\"></div>\\n  <div class=\\\"fixed -top-32 -right-32 h-96 w-96 bg-blue-600/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none\\\"></div>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Immersive UI\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Immersive UI\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"flex h-[768px] w-[1024px] flex-col bg-[#020617] text-slate-100 font-sans overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- Top Navigation Bar -->\\n  <nav class=\\\"flex h-16 w-full items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/80 px-8 backdrop-blur-md\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"h-8 w-8 rounded-lg bg-orange-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-black\\\">FF</div>\\n      <span class=\\\"text-xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase italic text-orange-500\\\">Guild Hub FF</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col items-end\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Logged in as</span>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-sm font-semibold text-orange-400\\\">KAPTEN_GARUDA <span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-orange-600/20 px-1.5 rounded border border-orange-500/30 ml-1\\\">KETUA</span></span>\\n      </div>\\n      <div class=\\\"h-10 w-10 rounded-full border-2 border-orange-500 p-0.5\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"h-full w-full rounded-full bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center\\\">ID</div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <!-- Main Content Layout -->\\n  <main class=\\\"flex flex-1 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <!-- Sidebar -->\\n    <aside class=\\\"w-64 border-r border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/50 p-6 flex flex-col gap-8\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col gap-1\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2\\\">Menu Utama</p>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg bg-orange-500/10 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-orange-500 border-l-2 border-orange-500\\\">\\n          Dashboard\\n        </button>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-800/50\\\">\\n          Daftar Anggota\\n        </button>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-800/50\\\">\\n          Pengumuman\\n        </button>\\n        <button class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 hover:bg-slate-800/50\\\">\\n          Pengaturan Guild\\n        </button>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"mt-auto rounded-xl bg-slate-900/80 p-4 border border-slate-800 shadow-lg\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1\\\">Guild ID</p>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-lg font-mono font-bold text-white\\\">FF-INDO-99</p>\\n        <button class=\\\"mt-3 w-full rounded bg-slate-800 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold hover:bg-slate-700 transition-colors uppercase\\\">Salin Link Invite</button>\\n      </div>\\n    </aside>\\n\\n    <!-- Content Area -->\\n    <section class=\\\"flex-1 p-8 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <!-- Stats Row -->\\n      <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-6\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"rounded-2xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-5 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute -right-2 -top-2 h-16 w-16 bg-blue-500/5 rounded-full blur-2xl\\\"></div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase\\\">Total Member</p>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-3xl font-black mt-1\\\">48<span class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-600 font-medium ml-1\\\">/ 50</span></h3>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"rounded-2xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-5 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute -right-2 -top-2 h-16 w-16 bg-orange-500/5 rounded-full blur-2xl\\\"></div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase\\\">Avg. Level</p>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-3xl font-black mt-1 text-orange-500\\\">LV. 64</h3>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"rounded-2xl bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-5 shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute -right-2 -top-2 h-16 w-16 bg-red-500/5 rounded-full blur-2xl\\\"></div>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase\\\">Tournament Win</p>\\n          <h3 class=\\\"text-3xl font-black mt-1 text-red-500\\\">12</h3>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Split Sections -->\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 grid grid-cols-5 gap-6 min-h-0\\\">\\n        <!-- Mading (Noticeboard) -->\\n        <div class=\\\"col-span-3 flex flex-col rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 px-6 py-4\\\">\\n            <h4 class=\\\"font-black uppercase italic tracking-wider text-orange-500\\\">Mading Guild</h4>\\n            <button class=\\\"rounded bg-orange-600 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-black uppercase text-black hover:bg-orange-500\\\">+ Tambah</button>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 p-6 space-y-4 overflow-y-auto\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-4\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2\\\">\\n                <h5 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-white\\\">Scrim Internal @ 20:00 WIB</h5>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">2 Jam Lalu</span>\\n              </div>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed italic\\\">Wajib hadir semua core team untuk persiapan Tourney Season depan. Map: Bermuda & Purgatory.</p>\\n              <div class=\\\"mt-3 flex gap-2\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\\\">#SCRIM</span>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] bg-red-500/10 text-red-400 px-2 py-0.5 rounded\\\">#IMPORTANT</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"rounded-xl bg-slate-800/40 border border-slate-700/50 p-4 opacity-75\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start mb-2\\\">\\n                <h5 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-tight\\\">Pendaftaran Tourney Regional</h5>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Kemarin</span>\\n              </div>\\n              <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed\\\">Silahkan hubungi Officer untuk pendaftaran slot 1 dan slot 2 paling lambat jam 10 malam ini.</p>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Member List -->\\n        <div class=\\\"col-span-2 flex flex-col rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 px-6 py-4\\\">\\n            <h4 class=\\\"font-black uppercase italic tracking-wider text-slate-400\\\">Daftar Anggota</h4>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 p-4 overflow-y-auto\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg bg-slate-800/30 p-3 border border-transparent hover:border-slate-700 transition-all\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n                  <div class=\\\"h-8 w-8 rounded bg-orange-500/20 text-orange-500 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs\\\">G</div>\\n                  <div>\\n                    <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">Garuda_Raja</p>\\n                    <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Jakarta \342\200\242 Lv. 72</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[9px] font-bold text-orange-500 bg-orange-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase\\\">Officer</span>\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg bg-slate-800/30 p-3 border border-transparent hover:border-slate-700 transition-all\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n                  <div class=\\\"h-8 w-8 rounded bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs\\\">M</div>\\n                  <div>\\n                    <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">Mist_Hunter</p>\\n                    <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Bandung \342\200\242 Lv. 65</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[9px] font-bold text-slate-500 bg-slate-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase\\\">Member</span>\\n              </div>\\n              <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg bg-slate-800/30 p-3 border border-transparent hover:border-slate-700 transition-all\\\">\\n                <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n                  <div class=\\\"h-8 w-8 rounded bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-xs\\\">S</div>\\n                  <div>\\n                    <p class=\\\"text-xs font-bold\\\">Sniper_Elite</p>\\n                    <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500\\\">Surabaya \342\200\242 Lv. 58</p>\\n                  </div>\\n                </div>\\n                <span class=\\\"text-[9px] font-bold text-slate-500 bg-slate-500/10 px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase\\\">Member</span>\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- Visual Overlay Background Elements (Simulated) -->\\n  <div class=\\\"fixed -bottom-32 -left-32 h-96 w-96 bg-orange-600/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none\\\"></div>\\n  <div class=\\\"fixed -top-32 -right-32 h-96 w-96 bg-blue-600/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none\\\"></div>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    }
  }
}
