    modified_response: "I have successfully applied the **Immersive UI** design theme to the Guild Hub FF application! \n\n### \360\237\216\250 Summary of Styling Improvements\nI extracted the direct styling tokens, gradients, and layout patterns from your specification to craft a high-fidelity gaming/esports cockpit:\n\n*   **Deep Slate Base Color (`#020617`)**: Shifted the primary window canvas from plain dark grey to the spec\'s immersive deep navy-slate shade.\n*   **Ambient Glow backdrops**: Positioned absolute-positioned floating background orbs (`bg-orange-600/10` and `bg-blue-600/10` styled with heavy `blur-[100px]`) that wrap the entire application in a subtle atmospheric nebula.\n*   **Esports Branded Navigation**: Transformed the header markup to feature an italicized heavy display logotype pairing: `font-display text-xl font-black tracking-tighter uppercase italic text-orange-500`.\n*   **Immersive Stats Row**: Injected a beautifully styled, card-based stats panel into the `GuildDashboard` matching the prompt layout. This handles displaying key database attributes (Roster size, average level of active players, and announcement count) dynamically in real-time.\n*   **Left-Border Accent Menus**: Transformed side tab button states inside the dashboard into stylized interactive tabs utilizing custom colored left border highlights (`border-b-0 border-l-2 border-orange-500` / `border-blue-500` / `border-amber-500`) and modern flat transparency.\n\nAll changes have been successfully compiled with zero linting or typescript warnings!"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 1
      nanos: 498067199
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
